  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>The chaotic, somewhat random design of your racial weapons makes it easy to combine them with illusions.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13, Combat Expertise, Gnome Weapon Focus, Improved Feint, base attack bonus +1, gnome magic and weapon familiarity racial traits.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>While feinting with a melee weapon that has 'gnome' in its name, you can sacrifice a spell slot, a spell of the illusion school, or a spell from the gnome magic racial trait to gain a bonus on the skill check attempted to feint. This bonus is equal to 1 + the level of the spell sacrificed. If you sacrifice a 0-level spell, you cannot cast or sacrifice that spell again for 24 hours.",
